                                                                                line-height: 24px;
                                                                                color: #333333;
                              ">
                            <p>

                              Dear <%- name %>,
                                <br><br>

                              We are excited to welcome you to TrustLog! As a registered <%- role %>, we are pleased to
                                provide you with the necessary information to access your account through our mobile
                                application.
                                <br><br>

                                Please find your account credentials below:
                                <br><br>

                                Username: <%- email %> <br>
                                  Password: <%- password %>

                                    <br><br>

                                    To access your TrustLog account via our mobile app, please follow these steps:
                                    <br><br>

                                    1. Download the TrustLog mobile app from the [App Store/Google Play Store]. <br>
                                    2. Open the app and tap on the "Login" button.<br>
                                    3. Enter your username and password provided above.<br>
                                    4. Tap on the "Login" or "Sign In" button to proceed.<br>
                                    5. Once logged in, you will have full access to the TrustLog mobile app and its
                                    features.<br>


                                    <br><br>
                                    Thank you for joining TrustLog! We believe your contributions will greatly enhance
                                    our platform, and we look forward to your success.
                                    <br><br>

                                    Best regards,<br>
                                    TrustLog
